facts.Perugia.forExpats="Perugia is a charming city in central Italy known for its rich history vibrant culture and stunning architecture with a good quality of life for expats. The city is situated on a hilltop offering breathtaking views of the surrounding countryside. Perugia is a must-visit destination for anyone interested in exploring Italy's cultural heritage. The city has a significant international population with many students and expats drawn to its universities and cultural events. Perugia is home to several public and private universities and colleges offering a wide range of courses and degrees. The city also has many international schools catering to the needs of expat families and children."
